SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"
INNER JOIN "Baskets" AS b ON t."Id" = b."Id"
INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON b."UserId" = a."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

2024-11-20 23:09:31.130 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (29ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

2024-11-20 23:12:08.036 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (11ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"
INNER JOIN "Baskets" AS b ON t."Id" = b."Id"
INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON b."UserId" = a."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"

) AS t

    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"

        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"
INNER JOIN "Baskets" AS b ON t."Id" = b."Id"
INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON b."UserId" = a."Id"

    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"

    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"
INNER JOIN "Baskets" AS b ON t."Id" = b."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"
INNER JOIN "Baskets" AS b ON t."Id" = b."Id"
INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON b."UserId" = a."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"

    WHERE (e."Code" = @__code_0) AND (m."Name" = @__menu_1)
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a."AppRolesId", a."EndPointsId", a0."Id", a0."ConcurrencyStamp", a0."Name", a0."NormalizedName"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EndPointsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."AppRolesId", t0."EndPointsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"

    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"
INNER JOIN "Baskets" AS b ON t."Id" = b."Id"
INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON b."UserId" = a."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0

        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"

    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"

    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedDate", t."OrderCode", (
    SELECT COALESCE(SUM(p."Price" * b0."Quantity"::bigint), 0.0)::bigint
    FROM "BasketItems" AS b0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON b0."ProductId" = p."Id"
    WHERE b."Id" = b0."BasketId") AS "TotalPrice", a."UserName", CASE
    WHEN (c."Id" IS NOT NULL) THEN TRUE
    ELSE FALSE
END AS "Completed"
FROM (
    SELECT o."Id", o."CreatedDate", o."OrderCode"
    FROM "Orders" AS o
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "ComplatedOrders" AS c ON t."Id" = c."OrderId"

SELECT t."Id", t."Name", t."Stock", t."Price", t0."Path", t0."Showcase", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId", t0."Id"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t1."Path", t1."Showcase", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", t1."Id"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."Path", f."Showcase"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS t1 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = t1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProductsId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."ProductImageFilesId", t0."ProductsId"
